>> Used in Dictionary

>> Searching a word is done in O(word length) time;

>> Very good in finding prefixes

>> Instead of maintaining a boolean for wordEnd -> Instead maintain a counter for each word -> So that we can maintain a counter on how many times the word is inserted;

>> Also using the prefix counter makes deletion of a node in trie easier.


Patterns


>> For counting and answer counts for prefixes ==> One way is to augument trie with counts while inserting